data.description: Location, Location! right in the heart of Chiefland. Lovely, Completely Remodeled, 3bd 2ba Concrete Block home with a bonus Area that could be used as a 4th bedroom. New Metal Roof, New AC, and All new beautiful Vinyl Plank flooring throughout. Brand New Beautiful Kitchen with white shaker cabinets,  Lovely granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Home features a Large great room / dining room combo, new lighting and custom blinds  throughout. Nice Large Utility/ Laundry room ! Spacious Master Bedroom has new French doors off the back. Both Bathrooms are beautifully  remodeled! Yard is fenced on 3 sides  with privacy fence off the back . Come take a tour at this home today, you will not be disappointed !
